ADVANCED CERAMIC April Sales Fall 23.90% (Table) : 3152 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-05-05T09:32:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/advanced-ceramic-april-sales-fall-23-90-table-3152-tt.html
ADVANCED CERAMIC said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 23.90% to NT$107,233,000 from NT$140,903,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            107,233          140,903    
YOY%             -23.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            357,446          494,942    
YOY%             -27.78% 
=================================================================
 